n7億人唔夠5000蚊年薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"702d79ff2829afeb9a140362cdffbc18b6279b67","tid":2439860,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:37:46.000Z","msg":"試當真<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"360144fee4190a0b23d2c8fc319d17cfdebcbac9","tid":2439860,"uid":257191,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:44:42.000Z","msg":"低志森真係好撚柒,救命.<br />\n依家係大陸佬都唔撚中意睇你拍嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244619ec037d4b7ed32df20b335aaaa7346a0938","tid":2439860,"uid":59929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:48:52.000Z","msg":"大陸電影(尤其低智森拍果啲) 出到外國就算其他華語地區如台灣香港都冇人睇<br />\n而有國際視野既電影<br />\n係美國加拿大等英語系國家 包括整個文明社會都有市場<br />\n唔會大過成個大灣區咩?<br />\n地球夠七十幾億人口 賺晒佢地錢唔係仲好?"},{"pid":"b697bd24c420e7a668b0c0bd8b67463dac86351d","tid":2439860,"uid":39710,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:49:36.000Z","msg":"收撚皮啦低智森"},{"pid":"2536fb79b87072140e1ea6ddd040565b9de4cf04","tid":2439860,"uid":274996,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:51:33.000Z","msg":"佢地唔明白，從一開始中國就冇諗過益其他人，包括香港人。睇外資就知道，利用完你就會一腳踢走你。"},{"pid":"ccf9a176732d57b4505b0e27fb11c0e1f1bed9ca","tid":2439860,"uid":141668,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:51:41.000Z","msg":"其實田雞算有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d730bd2d825d08f3dac6f562099143282878de44","tid":2439860,"uid":126510,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"f1bc873f40992483236e4c253dcaf34438969520","tid":2439860,"uid":51271,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:08:29.000Z","msg":"又係呢d1人1蚊點會窮嘅理由，信果個都on9"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:54:58.000Z","msg":"其實 1人1蚊 呢句錯唔晒，大灣區乃至中國市場確實大<br />\n<br />\n不過同中共謊言一樣，佢只係講你聽你半句<br />\n<br />\n後半句係 <span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\